計精子都係唔active<br />\n影響生育機率？"},{"pid":"c51b329f948d416000f81bb9efc382d6b63276b2","tid":381714,"uid":2786,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:30:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>但係當做完愛，內射左入子宮<br />\n都算係人體內，溫度高，咁計精子都係唔active<br />\n影響生育機率？</blockquote><br />\n制造精子既optimum temperature低體溫幾度<br />\n所以高溫係影響sperm production<br />\n唔係activity of sperm"},{"pid":"138c1221b20d785c5cef009358dab26e78af807d","tid":381714,"uid":128993,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:42:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果你要最快時間殺死一條生命<br />\n你會唔會打佢春袋先?</blockquote><br />\n咬爆佢春袋</blockquote><br />\n據聞話猩猩部落同另一隊猩猩部落打交，會咬甩或者扯甩敵對部落春袋，令對方無法有後代，同時保護本部落雌猩猩唔會懷有敵對部落的胎<br />\n<br />\n猩猩基因同人類相似，人類社會都有閹割行為</blockquote><br />\n戇鳩<br />\n啲科學長問過隻猩猩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />又會知會扯甩人地個袋係為左令對方無後代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呃飯食都唔好太過份 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"911401d86fd12c5495d21f037395cc3ccd32ae7c","tid":381714,"uid":15823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:42:17.000Z","msg":"咁複雜既人體緊係分左department 去做<br />\n最後integrate 埋就變左咁樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b83a0ee86fbc45edde1691e351c0bc18b94e713","tid":381714,"uid":74728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:49:12.000Z","msg":"進化論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6f24c901a9b48c243839c9f53f27886aff72742","tid":381714,"uid":8733,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-31T08:55:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真mode<br />\n因為精子儲放既地方唔可以太熱 太熱既話會令啲精子唔active<br />\n咁人既身體就好熱既 所以春袋生係出面 可以降低幾度既溫度<br />\n令啲精子更active<br />\n<br />\n利申 好似係</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a